1:02:54.120 --> 1:02:56.440
 a prophet, as well as Lao Kuan, who was like a priest,

1:02:56.440 --> 1:02:58.120
 who said, no, no, no, this is obviously a trick.

1:02:58.120 --> 1:02:59.880
 This is obviously a trick.

