1:25:21.600 --> 1:25:23.440
 and not proud of our prison system.

1:25:23.440 --> 1:25:25.240
 I think it's a huge stain on our nation.

1:25:25.240 --> 1:25:26.520
 I'm not proud of a lot of things.

